import { ChangeDetectionStrategy, Component, Input } from "@angular/core"; @Component({ selector: "app-top-app-bar", templateUrl: "./top-app-bar.component.html", styleUrls: ["./top-app-bar.component.scss"], changeDetection: ChangeDetectionStrategy.OnPush, }) export class TopAppBarComponent { @Input() headline: string = "Title"; @Input() show1stTrailingIcon: boolean = false; @Input() show3rdTrailingIcon: boolean = false; @Input() show2ndTrailingIcon: boolean = false; @Input() configuration: "Small centered" | "Small" | "Medium" | "Large" = "Small centered"; @Input() elevation: "flat" | "on-scroll" = "flat"; }
{{ headline }}
{{ headline }}
